{"article_id":"MGFtrNxW25sOqqWk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe hinted at an `` inappropriate relationship '' between President Donald Trump and Russia during a wide-ranging interview on CBS ' `` 60 Minutes ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that has already sparked calls for a congressional investigation .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Speaking to `` 60 Minutes '' correspondent Scott Pelley ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"McCabe said","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"the FBI had reasonable cause","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"to open a counterintelligence investigation into Trump 's connection with the Russian government , a potential national security threat ,","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"following the firing of then-FBI Director James Comey in May 2017 .","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein was `` not joking ''","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"when he offered to wear a wire into the White House","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to `` collect evidence '' into Trump 's motivation","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"for firing Comey .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"`` And the idea is ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"if the president committed obstruction of justice ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"fired the director of the FBI","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"to negatively impact or to shut down our investigation of Russia 's malign activity and possibly in support of his campaign ,","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"as a counterintelligence investigator , you have to ask yourself ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"'Why would a president of the United States do that ? ' ''","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"McCabe said on `` 60 Minutes . '' `` So all those same sorts of facts cause us to wonder","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"if there is an inappropriate relationship , a connection between this president and our most fearsome enemy , the government of Russia ? ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Asked by Pelley","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"if Trump is `` in league with the Russians , ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"McCabe said ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` I 'm saying","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that the FBI had reason","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"to investigate that .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Right - to investigate the existence of an investigation does n't mean someone is guilty .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"I would say , Scott ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"if we failed to open an investigation under those circumstances ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"we would n't be doing our jobs . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Prior to the airing of McCabe 's interview , Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-South Carolina , said Sunday","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"he planned to conduct a Senate investigation into what he characterized as `` an attempted bureaucratic coup . ''","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"`` We 're going to find out what happened here","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"and the only way","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"I know","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"to find out","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"is to call the people in under oath","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"and find out ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"through questioning ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"who 's telling the truth","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"because the underlying accusation is beyond stunning , ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Graham said on CBS","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"' `` Face the Nation . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Graham , the chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee , added","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that he would subpoena McCabe and Rosenstein","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"if they did not agree to testify voluntarily .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Via Twitter , Trump responded Thursday to the news of McCabe 's interview","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"by calling him a `` disgrace to the FBI and to our Country ''","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who was trying to pretend to be a `` poor little Angel . ''","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"He also repeated many of his past criticisms of McCabe ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"he says","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"helped start the `` Russia hoax ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and was biased in favor of Hillary Clinton .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"During the `` 60 Minutes '' interview , McCabe said","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Rosenstein resisted Trump 's insistence","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"of referencing Russia in a memo","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"to justify Comey 's firing","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"- `` And the president responded ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"' I understand that ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"I am asking you to put Russia in the memo anyway , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"he said -","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"and later raised the idea","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"of wearing a wire to the White House . ``","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"He said ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"\" I never get searched","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"when I go into the White House .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"I could easily wear a recording device .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"They wouldn ' t know","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"it was there , \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"McCabe said .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"`` Now , he was not joking .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"He was absolutely serious .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"And , in fact , he brought it up in the next meeting","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"we had . ''","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"He added ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"`` I never actually considered taking him up on the offer . ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"The Justice Department last September ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"responding to a New York Times report","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that first revealed the conversation ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"issued a statement from another official","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"who was in the room","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"and interpreted Rosenstein 's offer as sarcastic .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Asked during Sunday 's interview","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"if Rosenstein supported obstruction and counterintelligence investigations against Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"McCabe answered ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"`` Absolutely . ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"McCabe was fired from the Justice Department last March by then-Attorney General Jeff Sessions for `` an unauthorized disclosure to the news media and lacked candor","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"- including under oath -","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"on multiple occasions . ''","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"In the `` 60 Minutes '' interview , McCabe described his firing as politically motivated ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"telling Pelley","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"he was authorized to release information to the media .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Graham 's `` coup '' comment echoed criticisms from other Republicans and Trump supporters","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"who have long claimed","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"there is a `` deep state '' conspiracy of career Justice Department officials against the president .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"They believe","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"that the opening of special counsel Robert Mueller 's investigation into a potential conspiracy between the Trump campaign and Russians","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"trying to sway the 2016 election","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"is a part of that conspiracy .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"`` When is someone going to finally investigate the investa ( g ) tors ? ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"tweeted the president 's oldest son , Donald Trump Jr. , on Friday .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"`` If this isn ' t an attempted coup","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"I don ' t know what is .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Regardless of party","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"if you ' re not troubled by this ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"you ' re part of the problem . ''","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"In the `` 60 Minutes '' interview , McCabe recalled meeting with Trump","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"after the president had just fired Comey .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"`` I was speaking to the man","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"who had just run for the presidency , ''","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"McCabe said .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"`` And won the election for the presidency","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and who might have done so with the aid of the government of Russia , our most formidable adversary on the world stage . ''","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"`` And that was something","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that troubled me greatly , ''","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"When Pelley asked","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"how long after Comey 's firing he decided to begin an investigation into possible obstruction of justice by the president ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"McCabe replied ,","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"the next day , I met with the team","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"investigating the Russia cases","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"and I asked the team to go back and conduct an assessment","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"to determine","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"'Where are we with these efforts","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"and what steps do we need to take going forward ? ' ''","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"McCabe said","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"he was `` very concerned ''","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"and wanted to make sure","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"that he had `` the Russia case on absolutely solid ground , in an indelible fashion . ''","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"wanted to make sure","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"if he was `` removed quickly , or reassigned or fired ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"that the case could not be closed or vanish","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"without a trace in the night . ''","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"His book , \" The Threat :","depth":3},{"id":139,"text":"How the FBI Protects America in the Age of Terror and Trump , '' hit bookshelves on Tuesday .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":279,"left":0,"right":278,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":276,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":185,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":169,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":141,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":158,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":150,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":145,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":3,"right":144,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":4,"right":143,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":142,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":8,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":9,"right":147,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":10,"right":146,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":155,"right":156,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":13,"right":154,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":17